T1  - Evaluating the Reasoning Capabilities of Large Language Models for Medical Coding and Hospital Readmission Risk Stratification: Zero-Shot Prompting Approach
AU  - Naliyatthaliyazchayil, Parvati
AU  - Muthyala, Raajitha
AU  - Gichoya, Judy Wawira
AU  - Purkayastha, Saptarshi
JO  - Journal of Medical Internet Research
