T1  - Vision-language models in diagnostic imaging: review of technical advances, clinical validation, and practical deployment
AU  - Dutta, Niharika
AU  - Bose, Kartik
AU  - Syailendra, Emir
AU  - Chu, Linda
AU  - Gupta, Pankaj
